title: Return Of The Jedi (1983 Original Version)
description:
This is the original 1983 version. Aliens subs are hardcoded (custom soft English subs for the rest of the movie). Source is DVD presented in a letterbox format for old 4:3 televisions. That has been corrected.

After rescuing Han Solo from the palace of Jabba the Hutt, the Rebels attempt to destroy the Second Death Star, while Luke Skywalker tries to bring his father back to the Light Side of the Force. Rated PG
